fields.name: speaker
fields.description: Speakers are those whose voices predominate in a recorded or filmed resource. (This resource may be a transcription of that recording.)
fields.example: Participants in a recorded conversation, elicitation session, or informal narration would be termed Speakers. Audience members who do not participate beyond the occasional backchannel would be termed Responders.

fields.name: IU
fields.description: This column contains intonation units in speech
